729111f-b.title: Richmond: Manor Road - Benedict Avenue
729111f-b.text:
(1)
Manor Road, east side, between Benedict Ave. and Ningsley
Ave., showing the W.S. Van Clief mansion. The house is situated
200 feet back of the road.
July 7, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, another view.
July 7, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
